是指哪种？","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"臧萌","uid":"1008692","ctime":1591540009,"ip_address":"","comment_id":224767,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":5,"race_medal":0,"score":"5886502176","product_id":100052201,"comment_content":"技术型的公司和非技术性的公司，如何选择呢","like_count":1,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1008692,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/64/34/03335c4a.jpg","nickname":"臧萌","note":"","ucode":"5505C1516EDFD5","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":497602,"discussion_content":"非技术性的公司是指哪种？","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1591540009,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]},{"author":{"id":1751234,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/1a/b8/c2/d1904d74.jpg","nickname":"酸辣土豆丝","note":"","ucode":"0E3E4AFB31E1E6","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":280684,"discussion_content":"比如，以云计算作为产品来卖的公司和以云计算做了自己的依托，来支撑自己公司电商业务的公司，对职场人，应该怎么选择呢","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1591592819,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"","child_discussion_number":3,"child_discussions":[{"author":{"id":1008692,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/64/34/03335c4a.jpg","nickname":"臧萌","note":"","ucode":"5505C1516EDFD5","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":1751234,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/1a/b8/c2/d1904d74.jpg","nickname":"酸辣土豆丝","note":"","ucode":"0E3E4AFB31E1E6","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":281261,"discussion_content":"在我看来这都算技术性公司。不是越底层越高级。而是看解决的问题越高级，才越有价值。\n\n你说的俩方向，我觉得都是用技术，解决某个领域的问题。我觉得倒是可以从做产品还是做项目的角度来区分。\n\n产品是不断积累，深耕某个行业或者需求。我觉得这是比较好方向。项目更多的是重复堆积，行业积累较少。","likes_number":2,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1591702784,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":280684,"ip_address":""},"score":281261,"extra":""},{"author":{"id":1105774,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/df/6e/267bd6ee.jpg","nickname":"1900","note":"","ucode":"320D65D14817D3","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":true},"reply_author":{"id":1008692,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/64/34/03335c4a.jpg","nickname":"臧萌","note":"","ucode":"5505C1516EDFD5","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":286326,"discussion_content":"如何区分是做产品还是做项目呢？做业务和做平台的好像都可以认为是做产品吧？","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1593135491,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":281261,"ip_address":""},"score":286326,"extra":""},{"author":{"id":1008692,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/64/34/03335c4a.jpg","nickname":"臧萌","note":"","ucode":"5505C1516EDFD5","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":1105774,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/df/6e/267bd6ee.jpg","nickname":"1900","note":"","ucode":"320D65D14817D3","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":true},"discussion":{"id":286362,"discussion_content":"产品的生命周期更长，开发周期也更长，需求也更复杂。对应的，需要更好更细致的设计，以应对生命周期内可能的变化和增长。\n\n很多东西有比较明确的分界线。比如说，如果你在做一个数据库，那肯定是产品。如果是做一个电商的促销页面，那肯定是项目。\n\n但是有些单靠外表确实不是很好区分。比如说，做一个电商的退货功能，这算是产品还是业务？\n\n我的判断标准就是，如果一个东西，简单直接，没有什么变化，那就是更偏向项目。如果复杂，需要考虑未来的变化，需要应对各种不确定性，有非常专业的领域，没办法靠copy-paste大法搞定，没有太多现成的可以参考，那就是做产品。","likes_number":1,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1593148227,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":286326,"ip_address":""},"score":286362,"extra":""}]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":222995,"user_name":"王智","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1079657,"ip_address":"","ucode":"0335277F255F7A","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/79/69/5960a2af.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1590978525,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":"82204","content":"上升势头可能要看自己的眼光，但是下降势头还是很好看出来的，关注一下新闻，公司的发展，股价等等就差不多了。","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"臧萌","uid":"1008692","ctime":1590986930,"ip_address":"","comment_id":222995,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":"5885945821","product_id":100052201,"comment_content":"行业势头怎么判断呢? 技术的选择耗子叔有讲过,行业势头是要看各种大会吗? 还是凭借自己的客观主观的判断呢?这点感觉有点模糊.","like_count":2,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1008692,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/64/34/03335c4a.jpg","nickname":"臧萌","note":"","ucode":"5505C1516EDFD5","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":496983,"discussion_content":"上升势头可能要看自己的眼光，但是下降势头还是很好看出来的，关注一下新闻，公司的发展，股价等等就差不多了。","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1590986930,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":222937,"user_name":"Middleware","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1072015,"ip_address":"","ucode":"C0028293ECDD47","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/5b/8f/4b0ab5db.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1590971346,"is_pvip":true,"replies":[{"id":"82199","content":"哈哈哈哈哈，这个话题单拉出来可以开专栏对吧","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"臧萌","uid":"1008692","ctime":1590978324,"ip_address":"","comment_id":222937,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":3,"race_med